===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|bottle|lang=enm}}, {{term|botle|lang=enm}}, {{term|buttle|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|botl|lang=ang}}, {{term|bold||abode, house, dwelling-place, mansion, hall, castle, temple|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|budlan||buþlan||bōdlan||bōþlan|house, dwelling, farm|lang=en}}, from {{proto|Indo-European|bhōw-|to swell, grow, thrive, be, live, dwell|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{etyl|frr|-}} {{term|budel|lang=frr}}, {{term|bodel|lang=frr}}, {{term|bol|lang=frr}}, {{term|boel||dwelling, inheritable property|lang=frr}}, {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|boedel|lang=nl}}, {{term|boel||inheritance, estate|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|da|-}} {{term|bol||farm|lang=da}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|ból||dwelling, abode, farm, lair|lang=is}}. Related to {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|byldan||to build, construct|lang=ang}}. More at {{l|en|build}}.

