===Etymology 2===
{{etyl|xno}} and {{etyl|fro}} {{term|boteille}} (Modern French {{term|bouteille|lang=fr}}), from {{etyl|VL.}} *{{term||botticula}}, ultimately of disputed origin. Probably a diminutive of {{etyl|LL.}} {{term|buttis|lang=la}}.

